00:21:15.010 --> 00:21:17.950
you can't really
innovate very well.

00:21:17.950 --> 00:21:19.810
It's hard to
maintain facilities.

00:21:19.810 --> 00:21:22.580
KEVIN: But you said
they get a $20 billion--

00:21:22.580 --> 00:21:24.830
WILLIAM BONVILLIAN: They do
