00:22:46.782 --> 00:22:48.240
not to be able to
testify about it.

00:22:48.240 --> 00:22:49.907
This isn't a
national-security interest,

00:22:49.907 --> 00:22:51.540
in that it has to be protected.

00:22:51.540 --> 00:22:52.080
STEPH: Yeah.

